  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1011">
<l>karumattā ṉāṇuta ṉāṇut tirunuta </l>
<l>ṉallavar nāṇup piṟa</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>True modesty is the fear of (evil) deeds all other modesty is (simply) the bashfulness of virtuous maids.</l>
            </lg>
